      • DeviceDescriptionGenerator

        public DeviceDescriptionGenerator(int devNumber,
                                  long seed,
                                  java.io.File outputFile,
                                  double classAssertionProbability,
                                  org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntologyManager manager,
                                  org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLOntology ont,
                                  OntologyExtractor extractor)
        Constructor
        Parameters:
        devNumber - The number of device descriptions; 1 by default.
        seed - Random seed for generating randomized device descriptions; 0 by default.
        outputFile - Generated output ontology as file.
        classAssertionProbability - The probability of generating class assertion axiom for each named individual ([0, 1]); 0.5 by default.
        manager - Hold of an ontology manager.
        ont - Hold of input ontology.
        extractor - Ontology extractor used for extracting OWL axioms from input ontology.
